<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3410] Unable to set/modify TTL on a column family using the shell.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3410</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When attempting to set the TTL parameter on a column family using the HBase shell, the following error is reported and the parameter is not modified:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;hbase(main):042:0&amp;gt; create &apos;t1&apos;, &lt;/p&gt;
{NAME =&amp;gt; &apos;f1&apos;, VERSIONS =&amp;gt; 1, TTL =&amp;gt; 2592000, BLOCKCACHE =&amp;gt; true}

&lt;p&gt;ERROR: uninitialized constant Hbase::Admin::HColumnDescriptor&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;All&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12494593">HBASE-3410</key>
            <summary>Unable to set/modify TTL on a column family using the shell.</summary>
